{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"87ee8afcb8","title":"周恩来接见东北三省群众组织代表时的讲话（摘录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0aa5ee9537","index":0,"year":1967,"month":9,"day":28,"articleId":"87ee8afcb8"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6cb6d2ba4e","type":"title","text":"周恩来接见东北三省群众组织代表时的讲话（摘录）","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"87ee8afcb8"},{"id":"5bf9468819","type":"paragraph","text":"说过多少次了，“揪军内一小撮”是错误的，你们现在为什么还要揪军内一小撮？揪谁呢？揪沈阳军区？为什么要这样势不两立？","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"87ee8afcb8"},{"id":"f42c0b8659","type":"paragraph","text":"黄埔港有四五十条船停着，湛江港也这样，广州半个月没开出火车来，你们心里安不安？文化大革命已经进行了十五个月，再搞十五个月还行啊？还要放假闹革命、第三次大串联，大错特错嘛！","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"87ee8afcb8"}],"page":{"id":"5eef3c17c6","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"87ee8afcb8","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}